structure.unit: SCHOOL EMPLOYEES -- TEACHERS' RETIREMENT AND TENURE

law.history: Repealed 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 274, sec. 2, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 201, secs. 8 and 12.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Prohibition against solicitation or assessment, political activity or acceptance of compensation other than salary.
